                            <comment id="15936426" author="jking3" created="Wed, 22 Mar 2017 14:39:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am re-opening this issue because the fix was incomplete.  If the service method returns a structure, and the structure contains the ForeignInfo, then the structure is generated into Types.pm, and it also needs the &quot;use&quot; clauses or else it doesn&apos;t work.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15936445" author="jking3" created="Wed, 22 Mar 2017 14:50:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-4079&quot; title=&quot;Generated perl code that returns structures from included thrift files is missing a necessary use clause&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-4079&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-4079&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-reopened.tgz which extends the example to use a struct, forcing the same issue in the Types.pm generated time.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15936634" author="githubbot" created="Wed, 22 Mar 2017 16:35:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user jeking3 opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/thrift/pull/1219&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/thrift/pull/1219&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

